content:
Hello Khoa! Welcome to the Claude Agent SDK project. 

I'm here to help you with this full-stack chat application that has:
- A Python backend using Claude Agent SDK
- A Next.js frontend with shadcn/ui components
- Support for Skills, MCP servers, and Subagents

What would you like to work on today? I can help with:
- Backend development (FastAPI, Claude SDK integration)
- Frontend development (Next.js, React components)
- Adding new features or fixing bugs
- Configuration and setup
- Code review and optimization

Feel free to ask me anything!
